The '''Fel estate'''<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|I|259|Fel, Fyric}}</ref> was a large estate on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]], located near [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet City]]. It was granted to [[Soontir Fel/Legends|Soontir Fel]] by [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] after the former was granted the title of [[Baron of the Empire/Legends|Baron of the Empire]] following the [[Battle of Derra IV]]. [[Fel dynasty|Fel's entire family]] lived there.

